snippet.title: Lavender and Dragon Help Dimensional Silver and Blaze with Baby Delivery - VRChat
snippet.description:
NOTE: This happened hours before Tommy's race against Grant during the Tommy's Redemption Arc. Some scenes are cut due to "certain events" taking place and also because we were using VRChat. We did not have any baby avatars to use either.

Lavender had rushed to the hospital after receiving spam texts from Dimensional Silver about Dimensional Blaze going into labor. Due to her experience and being a mother of twins herself, she had arrived to help the two out along with Dragon the Hedgehog. Will everything go well? And will the babies and parents be alright? Most importantly, will Lavender be able to hold herself together due to her labor experience?

Dragon's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/XxDragonBladexX

Dimensional Silver's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCStJT0NEkAzmLLNpyVScD4w

Dimensional Blaze's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCb0P8a6hBlfOeP2hZ22pDHQ
